FBIS4-10221 "drlat069_a_94009" FBIS-LAT-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Dominican Republic Fortifies Border Dominican Republic Fortifies Border FL0804192694 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1700 GMT 8 Apr 94 FL0804192694 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [Text] The Dominican Republic will fortify its border with Haiti to stop the smuggling of fuel and other goods to that country. Haiti is currently facing an international embargo aimed at forcing the military to relinquish the power it wrested from Jean-Bertrand Aristide.
